<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title><![CDATA[Yasuhiro's blog]]></title><description><![CDATA[Introducing technology, Japanese culture and so forth.]]></description><link>https://yas-ito.com</link><generator>GatsbyJS</generator><lastBuildDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2020 10:24:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><item><title><![CDATA[How to add copy icon to code blocks of markdown for Gatsby with Typescript]]></title><description><![CDATA[Installing a plugin Adding plugin to gatsby-config.js You might be better to put "gatsby-remark-code-buttons" before "gatsby-remark-prismjs…]]></description><link>https://yas-ito.com/copy-icon-code/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://yas-ito.com/copy-icon-code/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 11 Jul 2020 21:40:32 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;h2&gt;Installing a plugin&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div
              class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-container&quot;
              data-toaster-id=&quot;8036456865865427000&quot;
              data-toaster-class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-toaster&quot;
              data-toaster-text-class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-toaster-text&quot;
              data-toaster-text=&quot;Copied to clipboard&quot;
              data-toaster-duration=&quot;5000&quot;
              onClick=&quot;copyToClipboard(`yarn add gatsby-remark-code-buttons`, `8036456865865427000`)&quot;
            &gt;
              &lt;div
                class=&quot;gatsby-code-button&quot;
                data-tooltip=&quot;Copy to clipboard&quot;
              &gt;
                &lt;svg class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-icon&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; width=&quot;24&quot; height=&quot;24&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill=&quot;none&quot; d=&quot;M0 0h24v24H0V0z&quot;/&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z&quot;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
              &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;yarn&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;add&lt;/span&gt; gatsby-remark-code-buttons&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Adding plugin to gatsby-config.js&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You might be better to put &quot;gatsby-remark-code-buttons&quot; before &quot;gatsby-remark-prismjs&quot;. In my case, when I put &quot;gatsby-remark-code-buttons&quot; after &quot;gatsby-remark-prismjs&quot;, it did not work for some reasons. I am not sure why it was happened.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div
              class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-container&quot;
              data-toaster-id=&quot;10282148164057880000&quot;
              data-toaster-class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-toaster&quot;
              data-toaster-text-class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-toaster-text&quot;
              data-toaster-text=&quot;Copied to clipboard&quot;
              data-toaster-duration=&quot;5000&quot;
              onClick=&quot;copyToClipboard(`    {
      resolve: \`gatsby-transformer-remark\`,
      options: {
        plugins: [
          {
            resolve: &amp;quot;gatsby-remark-code-buttons&amp;quot;,
            options: {
              tooltipText: \`Copy to clipboard\`,
              toasterText: &amp;quot;Copied to clipboard&amp;quot;,
              toasterDuration: 5000,
            },
          },
          // other plugins here
        ]
      }
    }`, `10282148164057880000`)&quot;
            &gt;
              &lt;div
                class=&quot;gatsby-code-button&quot;
                data-tooltip=&quot;Copy to clipboard&quot;
              &gt;
                &lt;svg class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-icon&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; width=&quot;24&quot; height=&quot;24&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill=&quot;none&quot; d=&quot;M0 0h24v24H0V0z&quot;/&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z&quot;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
              &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;js&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
      resolve&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token template-string&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token template-punctuation string&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;gatsby-transformer-remark&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token template-punctuation string&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
      options&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
        plugins&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;
          &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
            resolve&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;gatsby-remark-code-buttons&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
            options&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
              tooltipText&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token template-string&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token template-punctuation string&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;Copy to clipboard&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token template-punctuation string&quot;&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
              toasterText&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;Copied to clipboard&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
              toasterDuration&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;5000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
          &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
          &lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;// other plugins here&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Changing color and margin of the copy icons&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I created remark-copy.css under &quot;./src/styles/&quot;. But you can put the file anywhere you want.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div
              class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-container&quot;
              data-toaster-id=&quot;22064807579616640000&quot;
              data-toaster-class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-toaster&quot;
              data-toaster-text-class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-toaster-text&quot;
              data-toaster-text=&quot;Copied to clipboard&quot;
              data-toaster-duration=&quot;5000&quot;
              onClick=&quot;copyToClipboard(`.gatsby-code-button-container {
  touch-action: none;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: flex-end;
  position: relative;
  top: 28px;
  right: 3px;
  z-index: 100;
  pointer-events: none;
}

.gatsby-code-button-icon {
  display: block;
  width: 14px;
  height: 14px;
  fill: gray;
}`, `22064807579616640000`)&quot;
            &gt;
              &lt;div
                class=&quot;gatsby-code-button&quot;
                data-tooltip=&quot;Copy to clipboard&quot;
              &gt;
                &lt;svg class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-icon&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; width=&quot;24&quot; height=&quot;24&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill=&quot;none&quot; d=&quot;M0 0h24v24H0V0z&quot;/&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z&quot;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
              &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;css&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-css&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-css&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token selector&quot;&gt;.gatsby-code-button-container&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;touch-action&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; none&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;display&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; flex&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;justify-content&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; flex-end&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;position&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; relative&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;top&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; 28px&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;right&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; 3px&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;z-index&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; 100&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;pointer-events&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; none&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;token selector&quot;&gt;.gatsby-code-button-icon&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;display&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; block&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;width&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; 14px&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;height&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; 14px&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;token property&quot;&gt;fill&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; gray&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Import the plugin&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You need to add the below to gatsby-browser.js&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div
              class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-container&quot;
              data-toaster-id=&quot;87247013927257000000&quot;
              data-toaster-class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-toaster&quot;
              data-toaster-text-class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-toaster-text&quot;
              data-toaster-text=&quot;Copied to clipboard&quot;
              data-toaster-duration=&quot;5000&quot;
              onClick=&quot;copyToClipboard(`import &amp;quot;./src/styles/remark-copy.css&amp;quot;;`, `87247013927257000000`)&quot;
            &gt;
              &lt;div
                class=&quot;gatsby-code-button&quot;
                data-tooltip=&quot;Copy to clipboard&quot;
              &gt;
                &lt;svg class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-icon&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; width=&quot;24&quot; height=&quot;24&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill=&quot;none&quot; d=&quot;M0 0h24v24H0V0z&quot;/&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z&quot;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
              &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;js&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;./src/styles/remark-copy.css&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[Deploy Gatsby with Typescript to Netlify]]></title><description><![CDATA[It's easy to deploy Gatsby with Typescript to Netlify. You just need to follow the steps below: Getting gatsby cli and starter kid Creating…]]></description><link>https://yas-ito.com/gatsby-netlify-ts/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://yas-ito.com/gatsby-netlify-ts/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jul 2020 21:40:32 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s easy to deploy Gatsby with Typescript to Netlify. You just need to follow the steps below:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Getting gatsby cli and starter kid&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creating your repository on Github, Gitlab or Bitbucket&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creating your Netlify account and deploying to it&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uploading your blog&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using custom domain&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Getting gatsby cli and starter kid&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div
              class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-container&quot;
              data-toaster-id=&quot;79152991180767000000&quot;
              data-toaster-class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-toaster&quot;
              data-toaster-text-class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-toaster-text&quot;
              data-toaster-text=&quot;Copied to clipboard&quot;
              data-toaster-duration=&quot;5000&quot;
              onClick=&quot;copyToClipboard(`npm install -g gatsby-cli`, `79152991180767000000`)&quot;
            &gt;
              &lt;div
                class=&quot;gatsby-code-button&quot;
                data-tooltip=&quot;Copy to clipboard&quot;
              &gt;
                &lt;svg class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-icon&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; width=&quot;24&quot; height=&quot;24&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill=&quot;none&quot; d=&quot;M0 0h24v24H0V0z&quot;/&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z&quot;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
              &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;npm&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token function&quot;&gt;install&lt;/span&gt; -g gatsby-cli&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Getting starter kit&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div
              class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-container&quot;
              data-toaster-id=&quot;85000258821294620000&quot;
              data-toaster-class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-toaster&quot;
              data-toaster-text-class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-toaster-text&quot;
              data-toaster-text=&quot;Copied to clipboard&quot;
              data-toaster-duration=&quot;5000&quot;
              onClick=&quot;copyToClipboard(`gatsby new your-project-name https://github.com/gperl27/Gatsby-Starter-Blog-Typescript`, `85000258821294620000`)&quot;
            &gt;
              &lt;div
                class=&quot;gatsby-code-button&quot;
                data-tooltip=&quot;Copy to clipboard&quot;
              &gt;
                &lt;svg class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-icon&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; width=&quot;24&quot; height=&quot;24&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill=&quot;none&quot; d=&quot;M0 0h24v24H0V0z&quot;/&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z&quot;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
              &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;gatsby new your-project-name https://github.com/gperl27/Gatsby-Starter-Blog-Typescript&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you encounter &quot;Command failed with exit code 1: yarnpkg&quot; error, you should downgrade your node version for now. You can upgrade node version later, don&apos;t worry. In my case, node version 10.21.0 worked. Then, please retry to get starter kid.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Let&apos;s check it out.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div
              class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-container&quot;
              data-toaster-id=&quot;61734146494279660000&quot;
              data-toaster-class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-toaster&quot;
              data-toaster-text-class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-toaster-text&quot;
              data-toaster-text=&quot;Copied to clipboard&quot;
              data-toaster-duration=&quot;5000&quot;
              onClick=&quot;copyToClipboard(`cd your-project-name
gatsby develop`, `61734146494279660000`)&quot;
            &gt;
              &lt;div
                class=&quot;gatsby-code-button&quot;
                data-tooltip=&quot;Copy to clipboard&quot;
              &gt;
                &lt;svg class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-icon&quot; xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; width=&quot;24&quot; height=&quot;24&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill=&quot;none&quot; d=&quot;M0 0h24v24H0V0z&quot;/&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z&quot;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
              &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token builtin class-name&quot;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; your-project-name
gatsby develop&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span
      class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot;
      style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 702px; &quot;
    &gt;
      &lt;a
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-link&quot;
    href=&quot;/static/9482b238e45d53b31195ea08ae20f404/eb520/localhost-8000.jpg&quot;
    style=&quot;display: block&quot;
    target=&quot;_blank&quot;
    rel=&quot;noopener&quot;
  &gt;
    &lt;span
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot;
    style=&quot;padding-bottom: 126.13333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;
  &gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;picture&gt;
        &lt;source
          srcset=&quot;/static/9482b238e45d53b31195ea08ae20f404/e922d/localhost-8000.webp 375w,
/static/9482b238e45d53b31195ea08ae20f404/58c01/localhost-8000.webp 702w&quot;
          sizes=&quot;(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px&quot;
          type=&quot;image/webp&quot;
        /&gt;
        &lt;source
          srcset=&quot;/static/9482b238e45d53b31195ea08ae20f404/8a6f5/localhost-8000.jpg 375w,
/static/9482b238e45d53b31195ea08ae20f404/eb520/localhost-8000.jpg 702w&quot;
          sizes=&quot;(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px&quot;
          type=&quot;image/jpeg&quot;
        /&gt;
        &lt;img
          class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot;
          src=&quot;/static/9482b238e45d53b31195ea08ae20f404/eb520/localhost-8000.jpg&quot;
          alt=&quot;localhost&quot;
          title=&quot;localhost&quot;
          loading=&quot;lazy&quot;
          style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot;
        /&gt;
      &lt;/picture&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you downgraded node version to 10.x and want to use node version over 12.x, you can upgrade node version to 12.x, then:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div
              class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-container&quot;
              data-toaster-id=&quot;8318010850185908000&quot;
              data-toaster-class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-toaster&quot;
              data-toaster-text-class=&quot;gatsby-code-button-toaster-text&quot;
              data-toaster-text=&quot;Copied to clipboard&quot;
              data-toaster-duration=&quot;5000&quot;
              onClick=&quot;copyToClipboard(`rm -rf node_modules yarn.lock
yarn install
gatsby develop`, `8318010850185908000`)&quot;
            &gt;
              &lt;div
                class=&quot;gatsby-code-button&quot;
