&lt;h2&gt;Creating your repository on Github, Gitlab or Bitbucket&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can use Github, Gitlab or Bitbucket to manage and deploy your blog. It&apos;s free to use. You need to create your account on one of them first.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This time, I&apos;m using Github here.&lt;/p&gt;
