&lt;p&gt;You need to create repository for your project. If you don&apos;t know how to do it, please see &lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.github.com/en/enterprise/2.13/user/articles/creating-a-new-repository#:~:text=In%20the%20upper%2Dright%20corner,repository%20either%20public%20or%20private.&quot;&gt;Creating a new repository&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
